{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0114SvaygMAfXJ5FAF151CYf","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→Feature: Standard Preset Run Start Orchestration\n     2→  The `run start` command executes all stages of the standard flow preset\n     3→  end-to-end using the workflow engine, persisting validated payloads,\n     4→  rendered artifacts, journal events, and run snapshots at durable stage\n     5→  boundaries.\n     6→\n     7→  # SC-START-001\n     8→  Scenario: Happy path standard run completes all stages\n     9→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"alpha\" using flow \"standard\"\n    10→    And project \"alpha\" is selected as active\n    11→    And the run snapshot shows status \"not_started\" with no active run\n    12→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    13→    Then the command exits successfully\n    14→    And the run snapshot shows status \"completed\" with no active run\n    15→    And the journal contains \"run_started\", \"stage_entered\", \"stage_completed\", and \"run_completed\" events\n    16→    And payload and artifact records exist for all 8 standard stages\n    17→\n    18→  # SC-START-002\n    19→  Scenario: Run start succeeds for quick_dev flow preset\n    20→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"beta\" using flow \"quick_dev\"\n    21→    And project \"beta\" is selected as active\n    22→    And the run snapshot shows status \"not_started\" with no active run\n    23→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    24→    Then the command exits successfully\n    25→    And the run snapshot shows status \"completed\" with no active run\n    26→    And the journal records \"plan_and_implement\", \"review\", \"apply_fixes\", and \"final_review\" in sequence\n    27→    And payload and artifact records exist for all 4 quick_dev stages\n    28→\n    29→  # SC-START-003\n    30→  Scenario: Run start rejects already-running project\n    31→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"gamma\" using flow \"standard\"\n    32→    And project \"gamma\" is selected as active\n    33→    And the run snapshot shows status \"running\" with an active run\n    34→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    35→    Then the command fails with error containing \"not_started\"\n    36→    And the run snapshot is unchanged (still \"running\")\n    37→\n    38→  # SC-START-004\n    39→  Scenario: Run start rejects already-completed project\n    40→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"delta\" using flow \"standard\"\n    41→    And project \"delta\" is selected as active\n    42→    And the run snapshot shows status \"completed\" with no active run\n    43→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    44→    Then the command fails with error containing \"not_started\"\n    45→    And the run snapshot is unchanged (still \"completed\")\n    46→\n    47→  # SC-START-005\n    48→  Scenario: Run start validates workspace version before proceeding\n    49→    Given a workspace with unsupported version\n    50→    When the user runs \"run start\""}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01YWKh38fbHsxwHNSAPKt6Cz","session_id":"2cdec833-d9a4-4fe7-8fdf-432611cd39d7","uuid":"767247d1-e2f9-4e3c-8d6a-44d9c36081ed"}
