canning for state derivation\n- ✓ Atomic multi-file writes with rollback\n- ✓ Session storage for agent execution integration\n\n**Key Files Verified:**\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/fs.rs` (lines 1-1538)\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/requirements_drafting/model.rs`\n- `/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/requirements_drafting/service.rs`\n\nThe implementation is complete and compliant with Section 6 of the requirements specification."}],"totalDurationMs":51500,"totalTokens":45907,"totalToolUseCount":25,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":317,"cache_read_input_tokens":43985,"output_tokens":1605,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":317},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
